🇹🇷 🌴Marmaris (Turkey) 🌴🇹🇷
We are looking talanted artists:

✔️dancers- girls  (height from 165 sm)

with choreographic base for work in a show group at 5-star hotels in Marmaris (May - October; rehearsal time is April). Strictly no overweight!

The company provides:

✅ round-trip tickets;

✅ working visa;

✅ timely payment of salary;

✅ 2 days off per month;

✅ accommodation in  logdement with all conditions, 2 people per room;

✅ costumes;

✅ opportunity for extra-payment (Go-Go performances, different events, etc.)

✅ friendly team.

📩 For all details, please contact us in private messages (WhatsApp, Telegram +380953860793)

